1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,420
Muna da labarai a yanzu a Sydney inda jami'ai biyu suka tsere daga mummunan rauni bayan

2
00:00:04,420 --> 00:00:08,000
motar 'yan sanda ta yi hatsari kuma ta juye a yammacin birnin.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Ya sauka a kan rufinsa a Gilford da misalin karfe 5:30 na safiyar yau lokacin da 'yan sanda daga Auburn

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,480
suna amsa rahotanni game da maza da ke aikata abubuwa da ba su dace ba a cikin mota.

5
00:00:16,480 --> 00:00:18,960
Yanzu haka ana duba jami'an biyu a asibiti.

